{
  "texts": [
    "The input images of CKHK-22 were resized to 224 × 224 pixels, and all its values were normalized within a range of [0, 1] for consistency.",
    "All the CNNs were fine-tuned based on a batch size of 16 using an optimized learning rate of 0.0001 through Adam optimizer and loss function categorical cross-entropy for low classification errors.",
    "Moreover, to prevent overfitting at training, each model used a dropout rate of 0.3.",
    "Each of the CNNs was allowed to train up to a total of 100 epochs, with early stopping criteria on validation loss for avoiding unnecessary computation.",
    "Following that, the extracted features were then passed through the next stage for refinement."
  ]
}